subject:

FORGIVENESS
===================================================================
verse:
Therefore, if any one is in Christ, he is a new creation;
the old has gone, the new has come!” (II Cor. 5:17 NIV)

===================================================================
reflection:

Through forgiveness the arms of Jesus lift you, His blood
cleanse you, and His love changes you. It is His free gift
to you. Turn your heart to Jesus. Pray to receive Him and
His forgiveness by faith today. . . He will come into your
heart and make all things new. Do you have the joy of being
forgiven?

===================================================================
prayer:

Lord Jesus, thank You for the free gift of forgiveness that
lifts me, cleanses me, and changes me by Your love. I turn
my heart to You—come in, make me new, and fill me with the
joy of being forgiven. Help me to live each day in the
freedom and grace You have given. Amen. (AI)

===================================================================
